  "2377720": {
    "name": "Super Power Racing",
    "steam_appid": 2377720,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377720/extras/89c04639e14165b29e8f31c52c3e6530.avif?t=1771807238\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好体验一款令人热血沸腾的俯视视角街机赛车游戏吧！本作灵感源自你熟悉且喜爱的90年代经典赛车游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超级动力赛车联盟</strong>是一项享有盛誉的赛车赛事，来自世界各地的无情竞速者齐聚赛道，激烈角逐，以速度与力量冲向胜利的终点。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9辆可驾驶车辆（3辆初始车辆 + 6辆可解锁车辆）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7条赛道</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >街机模式 + 生涯模式（第1赛季）+ 驾驶学院（更多内容即将推出）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3种比赛模式（限时炸弹、极速竞赛、动力竞赛）+ 特别生涯赛事「Zombo Blast」</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377720/extras/0eb844319a4ac499cdb35c28200c4761.avif?t=1771807238\" width=595 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从驾驶学院开始，或直接进入精心设计的特别赛事，体验驾驶全新车辆的机会。赢得领奖台名次即可解锁街机模式中的新内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377720/extras/70aab4b9e50f37094e0bcdd17b6012eb.poster.avif?t=1771807238\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377720/extras/70aab4b9e50f37094e0bcdd17b6012eb.webm?t=1771807238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377720/extras/70aab4b9e50f37094e0bcdd17b6012eb.mp4?t=1771807238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377720/extras/6447579c11a0d678c1afb83794ad4ad6.avif?t=1771807238\" width=296 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁多种不同类型的车辆，从紧凑型汽车到漂移猛兽，甚至还有冰淇淋车！车辆可在生涯模式和街机模式中解锁，请查看解锁界面，了解如何解锁新内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377720/extras/0484a15bb09237a9b1cd92850b457b19.poster.avif?t=1771807238\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377720/extras/0484a15bb09237a9b1cd92850b457b19.webm?t=1771807238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377720/extras/0484a15bb09237a9b1cd92850b457b19.mp4?t=1771807238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
